@inproceedings{gao-etal-2023-livechat,
    title = "{L}ive{C}hat: A Large-Scale Personalized Dialogue Dataset Automatically Constructed from Live Streaming",
    author = "Gao, Jingsheng  and
      Lian, Yixin  and
      Zhou, Ziyi  and
      Fu, Yuzhuo  and
